Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... my favorite place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No one comes around this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... Do you always\Ndo battle here, Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah? N-No. I just got my cards recently too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The match against Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}was...\Nmy very first battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I was imagining training myself\Nwhile Midoriko gave me tips,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,to think of different battle situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't look at it so closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I was still unprepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The real battle was much different.\NI don't think I was ready for it yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then why do you want to battle me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You seemed weak,\Nso I thought it would be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... pretty straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! B-But, I really want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really trying her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If she wins the battle,\Nand gets closer to her wish, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Battling with Yuzu-pon!\NBattling with Yuzu-pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw! Energy Charge! Summon, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Battle Stone" "Amethyst"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If she uses that Peeping-something move,\NI'm gonna be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,With Amethyst's power,\NI'll banish R.F.R and attack Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll lay it on now before she\NGrows enough to use that move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch-y! You should be ashamed\Nfor being so aggressive-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my turn now. Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And now for a spell! It's card bye-bye time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Too Bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to toss your card away! Mmm... that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"Battle Stone" "Makuri" "Iron"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw... a level 1 card? So weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the type who wants to\Noverwhelm by going in numbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my choice how I fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just giving you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you have a red deck, it doesn't mean\Nyou should be super straightforward, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Your style of battle is\Ntoo straightforward, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so wrong with being straightforward?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,The field feels a lot warmer compared\Nto when I battled Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. It does feel different\Nfrom when I was battling Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The wind feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The field is a manifestation of\Nthe affinity between the Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Affinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, you're green, and Ruko is white...\Na pretty rare color.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,With both together, warm light is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel I can battle a lot more\Ncalmly now, Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san {\i0}and Midoriko-{\i1}san {\i0}are both really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}, please go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, okay. Um, draw...\NEner Charge. Tama, Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have any level 1 cards... Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose! Draw 2, Energy Charge!\NSummon, Mi-Ke and Mi-Ke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Mi-Ke, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This is so different compared to when\NI was playing at home with Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,My ears feel hot... I can feel the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...I feel excited too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:50.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow to level 2! Round, and Square!\NAttack Mi-Ke with Round, banish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack with Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Here she comes, Midoriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Again?! Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Use Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! Midoriko-{\i1}san{\i0}, level 2! Summon Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko Arts, Giant! Shiro's power\Ngains +5000 in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She seems to have lost heat all of a sudden.\NNow's your chance, Hitoe! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,...because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,My Ener isn't ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Arts, Peeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's finally going to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The move... It doesn't only discard my card...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...let me guess why Hitoe\Nwants to be an Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going to see... Find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with it being known.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish comes true,\Neveryone will find out anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Just brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, she's going to say\Nhorrible things to you using it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...your wish is nothing to be ashamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's toss out your level 1 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,And now... I'll take a peek into\Nyour wish. Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, look into her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Immoral...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Loves... her younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?! No way! That was her younger\Nbrother?! The pipsqueak with the same face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I know... I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding?!\NThat's super erotic! That's super pervy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,--Super immoral!\N--Sh-Shut... shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I know a word that describes this.\NDo you want to know the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I-N-C-E...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Dominating Fury!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! If you use such\Na burdening Arts now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop! Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...if I win, Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}'s wish won't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama? You... just spoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,No lose on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I want to win. Tama wants to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,On purpose? Were you planning\Nto lose on purpose, Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,If you did that, even if I win, I won't\Nbe happy. There's no meaning to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no use for me to hide it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I moved from Aomori to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I had an accent and was slow,\Nso I couldn't make any friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Uemura"\NBut then I got a letter from my friend in Aomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I read it over and over again, and... it saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"you'll be fine wherever you go, Hitoe-{\i1}chan{\i0}"\N"we'll always be friends" "let's play a lot again."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:11:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, a friend is a very beautiful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want to\Ntarnish my wish with cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best,\Nand attain my wish the right way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so neat, Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have any wish,\Nbut I want to battle with all I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... I'll battle with all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Good! Let's give it all we've got too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel the excitement swelling\Ninside... I just want to shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell, Oversize! Power-up all the SIGNIs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let that spell get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Anti-Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've felt this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...won?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Having a serious battle is... so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? The battle ended, but why\Naren't we being sent back to our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Evolved? Is this different from "Grow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The closer a Selector is to being an\NEternal Girl, the more we LRIGs gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,and become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, Tama! You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! You're speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She's in her stronger form\Neven when she's in her card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right... It looks like\Nthe words here are different too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}? Tama? I'm sorry\Nto have said that you looked weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You were both very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If I lose one more time, my wish\Nwon't come true. But, I won't regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait, I may regret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking maybe we can be friends,\Nwith all this Eternal Girl stuff aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I actually just moved here, and\NI couldn't make any friends either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But, when I finally made a friend, it felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I... no, you may not like it,\Nbut if you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Not like?! No! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you be a bit more quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm sorry!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'll think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She's already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:06.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so dark already.\NGrandma's going to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Pedestrians and vehicles only"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,My, a book about a card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"WIXOSS Card Encyclopedia" "Bookstore"\NMy, a book about a card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,This is quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"Sephirum" "Square" "Riot" "God Eater"\NEach card is carefully explained in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,There're a lot of cards I don't know here...\NThis one looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I met a girl today, and she was taking\Nnotes on the decks and battle flow simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm waiting for her answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me get that. Once dinner is ready,\Nlet Grandma take a look too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And we can battle after too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,With how Tama is now, I can add more red\Ncards and work them with the Search effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if I take out some cards, it'll become\Nweaker compared to Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s pure red deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle because it's fun. That's enough\Nfor now. But, if that's okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"Receiving"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Huh? Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?\NWhat's the matter? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san {\i0}hasn't come home yet?\NDid you get in touch with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,She hasn't phoned or emailed me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she would be at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, did you overdo yourself or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop being a try-hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it's about time\NI turn the tables. Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,If I had the Adamasphere that Kazuki\Nwas talking about, I could have retaliated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}! Finish them! Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you battle Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Why'd you battle her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you that you can't beat her\Nwith what you got now! Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.17,Main,,0,0,0,,--Shut up!\N--Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd never understand, Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd never understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I asked Momoka-{\i1}san{\i0}, and got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that why you met Momoka-{\i1}san {\i0}today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,She said that there was another\Ncustomer who was willing to trade it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,so Momoka-{\i1}san {\i0}worked it out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.92,Main,,0,0,0,,"Shining Battle Stone" "Adamasphere"\NWhy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If the trade didn't go well, I would've\Njust kept your hopes up for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I was so harsh on you, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you just started after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be stronger if you have that card,\NYuzuki. You've only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help too, so let's\Nget better together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you leave me alone for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}... Yuzuki-{\i1}san {\i0}must\Nbe really important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I was really weak and shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki was always there to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best to help\NYuzuki make her wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.61,Main,,0,0,0,,And when Yuzuki's wish comes true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I can finally say that I was able to help Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Kazuki... Why is he so kind to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,His kindness is making things more painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, you're late! Hurry and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking good, Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn... it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I've beaten Hitoe, and I've beaten Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,So why isn't anything changing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose three WIXOSS battles,\Nyou lose rights to enter in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how many times do you have\Nto win to become an Eternal Girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Just winning isn't enough to be an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,There are certain conditions\Nthat need to be met for each wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,So spill it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Say it, or else I'll rip you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You better say it now before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Tear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The hell! You're pissing me off!\NTalking all high n' mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The way you say things... reminds me of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... Enjoy the limelight while you still can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Iona? I just sensed Akira's battle.\NIt looks like she won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,She seemed pretty upset though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Iona? Let's just get rid of Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll feel good seeing\Nher cry. It'll be a spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop saying such brutish things...\Nor else I'll burn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Orichalcum, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it feels to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That feels so weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS is so... wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Wish Is Blasphemy."
